        <p>Analytics</p>
        <button type="submit" class="w3-button w3-block w3-black w3-margin-bottom">Select Plan</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-row-padding" id="about">
    <div class="w3-col l8 12">
      <h3>About</h3>
      <h6>Bybrisk, launched in 2019, caters to the logistics part of services and aims at providing a reliable and credible shipping experience for the people of Bhopal. Intending to bridge the gap between customers and services, we have partnered with more than 10 prestigious businesses in order to put them on a technological platform in such a short span of time. Perseverance and brand credibility being at the centre of our work model, we, at Bybrisk, quote the consumers with reasonable shipping charges and give fastest delivery assurance.

With intent to change the face of the hyperlocal market, Bybrisk has created efficient solutions for sellers and receivers to access leading logistic services encapsulated with commitment and vision. Bybrisk has got your shipping needs covered. </h6>
